      "weather": "Fine",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HAPPY CHICK (5) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by 5.5 lengths at this track in a handy 17.08 beating Paw Olive. One of the key runners again. WHY NOT AVA (3) made it two minor placings on the trot when beaten second (17.15) in a Grade 5 at this track last time out. Expected to bounce back to best. BIG PLAYER (1) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing seventh (35.66) in a Grade 5 NP at Sandown. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from six attempts. Should be in this for a long way. MAGIC THRILL (7) is always hard to beat when he races here at this trip.",
